00403             const bool Sort(
00404                     const int (*cmp)(const T&, const T&)    
00405 
00406                     )
00407             {
00408                 bool b_Result = true;
00409                 if (GetCount() < 2)
00410                 {
00411                     b_Result = true;
00412                 }
00413                 else
00414                 {
00415                     // Get a reference element.
00416                     T t_Ref = RemoveTail();
00417 
00418                     // Dispatch elements in q_1 and q_2.
00419                     Queue<T> q_1(0), q_2(0);
00420                     while (! IsEmpty())
00421                     {
00422                         T t_Sort = RemoveTail();
00423                         if (cmp(t_Sort, t_Ref) > 0)
00424                         {
00425                             q_1.AddTail(t_Sort);
00426                         }
00427                         else
00428                         {
00429                             q_2.AddTail(t_Sort);
00430                         }
00431                     }
00432 
00433                     // Sort each list q_1 and q_2
00434                     if (q_1.Sort(cmp) && q_2.Sort(cmp))
00435                     {
00436                         // Eventually restore q_1...
00437                         b_Result = true;
00438                         for (   Iterator it_1 = q_1.GetIterator();
00439                                 q_1.IsValid(it_1);
00440                                 q_1.MoveNext(it_1))
00441                         {
00442                             if (! AddTail(q_1.GetAt(it_1)))
00443                             {
00444                                 b_Result = false;
00445                             }
00446                         }
00447                         // ... then the reference element...
00448                         if (! AddTail(t_Ref))
00449                         {
00450                             b_Result = false;
00451                         }
00452                         // ... and then q_2.
00453                         for (   Iterator it_2 = q_2.GetIterator();
00454                                 q_2.IsValid(it_2);
00455                                 q_2.MoveNext(it_2))
00456                         {
00457                             if (! AddTail(q_2.GetAt(it_2)))
00458                             {
00459                                 b_Result = false;
00460                             }
00461                         }
00462                     }
00463                 }
00464                 return b_Result;
00465             }
